text: Crossotus sublineatus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Gestro in 1892. It is known from Chad, Algeria, Mauritania, Djibouti, Ethiopia, Somalia, Mali, Morocco, Kenya, Niger, Senegal, and Sudan.BioLib.cz - Crossotus sublineatus.
